---
import MainLayout from '@/layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout
  title="AIUXSLabs — Free AI Tools for SMB, Ecommerce & B2B Automation"
  description="Use free AI tools to make faster business decisions: calculate AI ROI, find Shopify break-even ROAS, and generate SOPs your team can execute."
  canonicalPath="/"
>
  <section class="rounded-[28px] bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-50 via-white to-white p-8 sm:p-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">Free AI Tools for SMB, Ecommerce, and B2B Teams</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-700">Free AI business tools for SMB growth.</p>
    <div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/ai-roi-calculator" class="rounded-xl bg-brand-600 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-white no-underline shadow-sm">Open AI ROI Calculator</a>
      <a href="#tools" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-5 py-3 font-semibold no-underline">See all tools</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="tools" class="mt-8 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
    <article class="rounded-[28px] bg-gradient-to-b from-sky-100 to-sky-50 p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-sky-200">
      <div class="mb-5 inline-flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white text-2xl shadow-sm">📈</div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">AI ROI Calculator</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-700">Estimate payback and ROI horizons from AI adoption decisions.</p>
      <a class="mt-5 inline-block font-semibold text-slate-900" href="/ai-roi-calculator">Use tool</a>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-[28px] bg-gradient-to-b from-teal-100 to-teal-50 p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-teal-200">
      <div class="mb-5 inline-flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white text-2xl shadow-sm">💹</div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Shopify ROAS Calculator</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-700">Find your break-even ROAS, CPA, and realistic profitability range.</p>
      <a class="mt-5 inline-block font-semibold text-slate-900" href="/shopify-roas-calculator">Use tool</a>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-[28px] bg-gradient-to-b from-emerald-100 to-emerald-50 p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-emerald-200">
      <div class="mb-5 inline-flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white text-2xl shadow-sm">🧩</div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">SOP Generator</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-700">Turn messy process notes into consistent SOP drafts your team can run.</p>
      <a class="mt-5 inline-block font-semibold text-slate-900" href="/sop-generator">Use tool</a>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <article class="rounded-[28px] bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-50 to-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-brand-100">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Who it’s for</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-slate-700">
        <li>SMB owners</li>
        <li>Ecommerce operators</li>
        <li>B2B teams and agencies</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-[28px] bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-100 to-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">How it works</h2>
      <ol class="mt-4 list-decimal space-y-1 pl-5 text-slate-700">
        <li>Pick tool</li>
        <li>Input numbers/context</li>
        <li>Get actionable output</li>
      </ol>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-8 rounded-[28px] bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-100 to-brand-50 p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-brand-200">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Proof & trust</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-slate-700">Built for practical decisions, not vanity metrics.</p>
    <div class="mt-4 grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/80 p-4 ring-1 ring-brand-100">
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">Estimate AI investment payback before rollout.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/80 p-4 ring-1 ring-brand-100">
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">Set profitable ad targets before scaling spend.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/80 p-4 ring-1 ring-brand-100">
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">Standardize operations with repeatable SOP templates.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-8 rounded-[28px] bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Explore more resources</h2>
    <div class="mt-4 grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-3">
      <a href="/ai-roi-calculator" class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-4 font-medium no-underline ring-1 ring-slate-200">ROI guides</a>
      <a href="/shopify-roas-calculator" class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-4 font-medium no-underline ring-1 ring-slate-200">Ecommerce profitability</a>
      <a href="/sop-generator" class="rounded-xl bg-slate-50 p-4 font-medium no-underline ring-1 ring-slate-200">SOP automation playbooks</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-8 rounded-[28px] bg-brand-700 p-8 text-white">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Start with AI ROI Calculator</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-brand-50">Validate impact first, then prioritize the highest-return workflows.</p>
    <a href="/ai-roi-calculator" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-xl bg-white px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-brand-700 no-underline">Start now</a>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
